description: The oldest and most famous full-service meat market in Minneapolis is now taking their marvelous meaty eats through the streets, and local foodies find that there’s really no finer way to dine. The menu at this truck features a mouthwatering selection of BBQ, Burgers, Sandwiches, and more! And of course it's all made with their very own premium Beef, Poultry, and Pork. This is why Minneapolis folk keep lining up to fork into all this fantastic fare. So if you’re craving the best of the deli right in your belly, be sure to visit Finer Meats & Eats.
name: Finer Meats & Eats
